{"tid":308940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個阿爺阿嬤嘅有趣事","createTime":"2017-07-04T14:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T19:15:31.000Z","uid":17845,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58ceb63f21e31f1dc32c7e393cf7ed9dfa823cf1","tid":308940,"uid":17845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"我阿爺當阿嬤鬧佢個陣就會熄咗個助聽器，扮唔知。"},{"pid":"be2f47bf582b671e19d4298a3026e115bbffa594","tid":308940,"uid":38194,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"係朋友個朋友度聽返黎：<br />\n<br />\n話說有一晚，嗰位朋友同屋企人食完飯之後車埋佢爸爸媽媽同阿嘛返屋企，忽然之間嗰位阿嘛指着前面大叫「有妖孽，有妖孽呀」，嗰位朋友即刻嚇撚左一跳話「唔係咁邪啊嘛」，之後佢爸爸同佢講「你又唔係唔知你阿嘛講嘢有鄉音，佢話前面有油入啊」"},{"pid":"eb24672c76229169fa489a5540b1edb01c340a28","tid":308940,"uid":104685,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"嫲嫲試過拎盒避孕套比老豆, 同佢講: 拎盒糖返去比乖孫食啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc43081bbbf2b77b922658c49f10a64905d0d5","tid":308940,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嫲嫲試過拎盒避孕套比老豆, 同佢講: 拎盒糖返去比乖孫食啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d62d4c3b0dc655989632bd6d24a055ed7149628","tid":308940,"uid":126232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我姑姐細個嗰陣好少同人講自己真名，攞身分證之後又即刻改咗個名， 阿爺好興一大班人嘅時候借啲意爆姑姐真名叫「梁金妹」"},{"pid":"2930fd44decef94b3a3e3d65bff41b4b4334fb29","tid":308940,"uid":51981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"阿公話細個讀寄宿學校 晚餐有兩個饅頭<br />\n咁佢同佢d fd都好唔鐘意食饅頭既 所以晚晚都將饅頭dum入廁所<br />\n結果有日個廁所終於塞左 個校長搵人通渠<br />\n一通所有饅頭爆返上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次諗起屎坑爆饅頭呢個畫面都好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22939e81164209005ebb4ce6d25755d13d04b2d","tid":308940,"uid":64308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"成家人食飯好興問潮州話點講<br />\n咁啱嗰次問緊唔同種類嘅魚<br />\n因為嗰時食緊飯 有唔同魚<br />\n跟住呀嫲就教乜胡(魚)物胡啦<br />\n之後有人問:嫲嫲 咁鯨魚點講呀<br />\n嫲:潮州冇鯨魚架<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fa3d8b6f220ace150154981c4cb168aba702d0","tid":308940,"uid":71216,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"阿婆同姑太嘅得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個加埋隨時150歲<br />\n話說喺鄉下有位親戚走咗搞緊喪禮<br />\n我阿婆返到鄉下準備嗰陣見到我姑太拎住個大袋就問<br />\n阿婆：乜要買嘢過去㗎咩？<br />\n姑太：(大良話)買heh！(即係買閪！)<br />\n阿婆：(大良話)乜有個嘅賣㗎咩？<br />\n（乜有呢樣嘢賣㗎咩？）<br />\n姑太：(大良話)有~阿明上日咪買hell囉～<br />\n（有~阿明上日咪買咗囉）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想像下兩個加埋150嘅老人家轉數咁快，真係冇得頂"},{"pid":"bf1e5a0cead7d72b5f0aff848084f43e3c7ce2ad","tid":308940,"uid":73762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成家人食飯好興問潮州話點講<br />\n咁啱嗰次問緊唔同種類嘅魚<br />\n因為嗰時食緊飯 有唔同魚<br />\n跟住呀嫲就教乜胡(魚)物胡啦<br />\n之後有人問:嫲嫲 咁鯨魚點講呀<br />\n嫲:潮州冇鯨魚架<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c46134df13b55a0858cf41fb326d6beddcb9a00","tid":308940,"uid":79706,"like":0,"disli